en.title: Full House at Malay BEP, Headquarter, 24th March 2009!
en.content:
FusionExcel's Malay BEPs at Headquarter have been attracting FULL HOUSE crowds every Tuesday night. On Tuesday 24th March 2009, the Malay BEP was graced by not one, not two but THREE of FusionExcel's Spokespersons, namely, Shalin Zulkifli (World Bowling Champion), Safee Sali (Malaysia's National Football Team Striker) and Wong Hong (Champion Bodybuilder). Shalin, Safee and Wong Hong shared their testimonials from using FusionExcel's Quantum Pendant with the enthusiastic audience. MC for the night is FusionExcel's Executive Director Azizuddin Abd Malik and speakers were FusionExcel's dynamic Presidential Director Dr Mohd Fadil and Director Mat Jutawan. A BIG THANK YOU to Aziz, Dr Fadil and Mat for a great job done! 

SEE YOU AT THE TOP!
